{"tid":1817700,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【阻你一分鐘】論POPO解鎖電話件事嘅嚴重性","createTime":"2020-01-09T10:03:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-10T06:33:09.000Z","uid":160537,"like":56,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"0ef835b974f8694c84ea3bba0f5879deffa94dab","tid":1817700,"uid":160537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T10:03:09.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">POPO解鎖電話嘅影響係非常嚴重！</span></div><br />\n<br />\n假如電話被解鎖，即使被捕手足如何清除資料或更改密碼，<span style=\"color: red;\">只要手機保持offline POPO依然可以睇到手機通訊內容</span>，例如Telegram, Whatsapp。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果POPO掌握到通訊內容，被捕手足<span style=\"color: red;\">及其朋友</span>被起訴的風險會較高。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">平平無奇的對話內容幫助popo搵證據</span>。例子如下：<br />\n<br />\n一、喺其他衝突日子同朋友<span style=\"color: red;\">報到</span>。每隔兩三小時會打「Safe」。即使被捕原因係鳩拉，popo都可以鎖定邊日你有岀過街發夢。甚至係話「好彩跑得快 等陣喺灣仔橋下等」咁就可以幫助popo收窄範圍。<br />\n<br />\n二、同很熟的戰友（有common勇武行動grp）（保持offline 被踢group都冇用）嘅日常對話。例如<span style=\"color: red;\">約食飯</span>。對返CCTV 咁勇武小隊嘅戰友樣就可以被鎖定。<br />\n<br />\n三、9up嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">激進言論</span>對被捕人士不利。例如曾經講過「黑警死全家」或更激進言論 「用火魔點點點」，證明到被捕手足對popo有仇恨之心。假設被捕手足極力否認火魔唔屬於佢 官未必信。<br />\n<br />\n四、<span style=\"color: red;\">通訊錄害手足</span>。即使telegram 可以設定做唔顯示電話號碼，但我哋都會set對方名。可能喺TG我set一個現實best friend + 前線手足做 Tom , 咁popo就可以對返手機通訊錄邊個叫tom. <br />\n<br />\n五、等等<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">解決方法</div></span></span><br />\n一、用太空卡加另一部電話 <br />\n二、每日清除所有日常對話。行動當日每半小時清對話。<br />\n三、打機內容<span style=\"color: red;\">只</span>在TG到傾 唔好喺IG又口多多<br />\n四、重要嘢用online game chat room傾都得 TG未必百份百安全<br />\n五、lock sim card/ vpn基本啦<br />\n六、用暗號 <br />\n簡單版例如星期三 1800見= 星期四 1900. (+1, +1)// 帶唔帶Mcdonald? (=Mask) <br />\n七、TG名同通訊錄名要完全唔關事<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">總結：</span><br />\n一、自己減低對自己不利的東西<br />\n二、自己減低對手足不利的東西<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n煲底見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11c78185ee6de335c7330b85e16c8b11bb660ea7","tid":1817700,"uid":160537,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T10:04:13.000Z","msg":"幫我推吓 阻你一分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a3432ee63dd24d27183ba18ad069ce581c0ce9e","tid":1817700,"uid":160537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T10:05:40.000Z","msg":"入嚟推吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f0094b38306c0c0e0624ddcb19304845a7a1364","tid":1817700,"uid":160537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T10:07:23.000Z","msg":"冇人推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c85255e6a80ce4531b4621141d04aabf45e8c1f6","tid":1817700,"uid":329698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T10:07:25.000Z","msg":"第三個點咪全世界都瀨嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27d5b77fc6a2f7eff524b958d25b6eae91a374b4","tid":1817700,"uid":83557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T10:09:57.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d62b67926bd63bd21b33b23112360e7e2c77364c","tid":1817700,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T10:10:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a9c70490465fa1588de66040cb31fe0be098f04a","tid":1817700,"uid":160537,